title: Philadelphia Outlasts Atlanta, and Which Games to Watch | GM Street (Ep. 296)
description:
The Ringer's Michael Lombardi and Tate Frazier take a look at the Eagles' defeat of the Falcons in the NFL season opener (02:00), and then give five intriguing matchups to watch for during Week 1 (22:00).
